<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_150" id="75r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_150_r2l11">Graf Johanſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l12">von wertheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l13"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> Als vns ewr gnade vormals von Meiſter Claſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l14">Parbẏrers wegen
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat / Darümb iſt derſelb
                        Meiſter Clas </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l15">yecʒund für vns kumen / vnd hat vns gebeten
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell von
                            <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l16">wegen cʒubiten vnd
                            <expan>cʒuverſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . daʒ Jr Jm
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade beweiſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l17">vnd Jm <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> gerawmen cʒug
                        vnd friſt / <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / Alſo
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l18">daʒ Jr das alſo durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        vvillen tun vvöllet / <expan>Alſu<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l19">das füglich ſeẏ / das wöllen vvir v̈mb ewr gnade
                                <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>d<ex>ienen</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l20"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ṽ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>ıcam</expan>
<expan>M<ex>isericord</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nj</expan> Anno etc xv<hi rend="sup">to</hi> $ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_150" id="75r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Graf Johansen von Wertheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr gnade vormals von meister Clasen
                        Parbyrers wegen <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat, darümb ist
                        derselb meister Clas yeczund für uns kumen und hat uns gebeten,
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell von
                            <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> wegen czu biten und <expan>czu
                                verschreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz ir im <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        gnade beweisen und im <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> gerawmen czug und frist
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. Also
                            <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir das also durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen tun wöllet,
                                <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell das füglich sey; das wöllen wir ümb ewr
                        gnade <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>d<ex>ienen</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> v <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>icam</expan>
<expan>m<ex>isericord</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>ni</expan> anno etc. xv<hi rend="sup">to</hi>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
